question: Show all graphic design tools and web design tools which need a subscription.
sql_query1:
SELECT Digital_Tools.Name 
FROM Digital_Tools
WHERE (Digital_Tools.Category = "Graphic Design" OR Digital_Tools.Category = "Web Design") AND Digital_Tools.Access = "Subscription"
sql_query2:
SELECT Digital_Tools.Name 
FROM Digital_Tools
WHERE Digital_Tools.Category = "Graphic Design" OR Digital_Tools.Category = "Web Design" AND Digital_Tools.Access = "Subscription"
interpretation1: Show all the subscription-based graphic- and web-design digital tools.
interpretation2: Show all the graphic design tools, also show the web design tools that run on a subscription model.
